data.description: Hurry and come see this beautiful, “Ready for Occupancy Now”, waterfront access home that has been updated in 2020. No hurricane or flood damage here. This wonderful 2-bedroom 2 bath home sits high and dry with a wonderful view of the Pease River with endless sunsets. This home has tile throughout, Master shower & tub replaced 2020. Kitchen cabinets & Renovation 2021. Dishwasher new 2019.  GE washer & dryer 2021. Water softener new 2022. Stove 2019. Septic Replaced 2021. Both Bedrooms renovated 2019. A/C has just been serviced March 2023. This Home also 2 waterfront lots “Not attached”. There is an optional HOA that gives you access to the Clubhouse with lots of open waterfront space for weddings, parties and gatherings Location and Boat Ramp.
